data.title: Mohit Malhotra's Entry
data.meta_description: Read Mohit Malhotra's Entry from the story It's All About Manan (On Hold)  by sweetybh with 674 reads. dhrulya, manan, fab5. Firstly sorry guys for updating la...
data.text:
Firstly sorry guys for updating late....

Hope you forgive me...

Apologies once again...

After the break up...

Nandini reached her home crying she started breaking all the things that were there in her room...

She still kept murmuring that all this happened to manik because of her...

She was so angry that she picked up a knife from the dressing table and was about to cut her wrist... When sm1 throws away the knife... N that is non other than Mohit Malhotra... (how many of you all thought it's manik) (raise ur hands)

She hugged Mohit n cried alot...

After few hrs she stopped crying...

On the other hand...

Manik is thinking of few to ways to get Nandini back.... He took help of fab 4 n the plan will be disclosed in the upcoming part...

So mission nandini manao... All keep their hands together.. I. E manik n fab 4 n navbhi....

All shout yes...
